# Contact Form Script

This script provides a simple contact form with backend validation and submission handling using CORE PHP. It also includes integration with Google reCAPTCHA to prevent spam submissions.

## Features

- HTML form with fields for Full Name, Phone Number, Email, Subject, and Message.
- Backend validation of form fields to ensure correct and valid input.
- Integration with Google reCAPTCHA to prevent bot submissions.
- Rate limiting to prevent spam submissions from the same IP address.
- Secure handling of form submissions using prepared statements to prevent SQL injection attacks.
- Email notification to the site owner upon successful form submission.
- Error handling for invalid input and submission failures.

## Prerequisites

- Web server (e.g., Apache,) with PHP support.
- MySQL database server.
- Google reCAPTCHA site and secret keys.
